cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on trajectory optimization for a dual-arm PR2 robot. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a memory of motion based on function approximators and dimensionality reduction techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper compares different function approximators and uses an ensemble method. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the PR2 robot may use vision-based sensing for motion planning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but relevant as the paper deals with motion planning for a robotic system.
